text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits obsolete IRM 2.152.1, Data Engineering, Data Engineering Policy.

Removed and obsoleted Data Engineering, Data Engineering Policy, dated August 19, 2019, due to the IRM Restructure within ACIO Enterprise Service, Solution Engineering Division to incorporate this policy into new Engineering Policy.
All projects following the Enterprise Life Cycle (ELC), and all applications that use the Data Management Service.
